fields.name: AssociatedResourceIds
fields.description: The list of resource IDs for the other Microsoft.NetworkCloud resources that have attached this network.

fields.name: ClusterId
fields.description: The resource ID of the Network Cloud cluster this trunked network is associated with.

fields.name: DetailedStatus
fields.description: The more detailed status of the trunked network.

fields.name: DetailedStatusMessage
fields.description: The descriptive message about the current detailed status.

fields.name: HybridAksClustersAssociatedIds
fields.description: Field Deprecated. These fields will be empty/omitted. The list of Hybrid AKS cluster resource IDs that are associated with this trunked network.

fields.name: HybridAksPluginType
fields.description: Field Deprecated. The field was previously optional, now it will have no defined behavior and will be ignored. The network plugin type for Hybrid AKS.

fields.name: InterfaceName
fields.description: The default interface name for this trunked network in the virtual machine. This name can be overridden by the name supplied in the network attachment configuration of that virtual machine.

fields.name: IsolationDomainIds
fields.description: The list of resource IDs representing the Network Fabric isolation domains. It can be any combination of l2IsolationDomain and l3IsolationDomain resources.

fields.name: ProvisioningState
fields.description: The provisioning state of the trunked network.

fields.name: VirtualMachinesAssociatedIds
fields.description: Field Deprecated. These fields will be empty/omitted. The list of virtual machine resource IDs, excluding any Hybrid AKS virtual machines, that are currently using this trunked network.

fields.name: Vlans
fields.description: The list of vlans that are selected from the isolation domains for trunking.
